snippet.title: God of War: Ascension™ Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/god-of-war/?emcid=or-1s-412983

God of War® fans rejoice! Infamous Spartan warrior Kratos is preparing to return to the PlayStation®3 system. This brand new trailer marks the official unveiling to the world of forthcoming game, God of War: Ascension™.

The most ambitious God of War adventure in the series so far, God of War: Ascension takes us right back to where it all began. Discover the origins of Kratos as he takes his first steps on a now legendary quest for freedom and vengeance.

Visit www.godofwar.com for more details, and like God of War on Facebook.com/PlayStation to stay up to date with the latest GoW announcements.

Rated Mature: Blood and gore, intense violence, nudity, and sexual content

©2012 Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC. God of War: Ascension is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC.
